Or foundations"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The princes of Zoan are complete fools; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 13:22","book":"Num","chapter":13,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 78:12","book":"Psa","chapter":78,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 78:43","book":"Psa","chapter":78,"verse":43,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 30:4","book":"Isa","chapter":30,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" Pharaoh’s wisest advisers give stupid advice!"},{"kind":"text","text":" How can you say to Pharaoh,"},{"kind":"text","text":" “I am one "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit a son"},{"kind":"text","text":" of the wise,"},{"kind":"text","text":" a student of eastern "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit a son of ancient"},{"kind":"text","text":" kings”?"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 13:22","book":"Num","chapter":13,"verse":22},{"label":"Ps 78:12","book":"Psa","chapter":78,"verse":12},{"label":"Ps 78:43","book":"Psa","chapter":78,"verse":43},{"label":"Is 30:4","book":"Isa","chapter":30,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit a son"},{"marker":1,"text":"Lit a son of ancient"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Where then are your wise men?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Let them tell you and reveal"},{"kind":"text","text":" what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies has planned against Egypt."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The princes of Zoan have been fools;"},{"kind":"text","text":" the princes of Memphis are deceived. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 2:16","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 46:14","book":"Jer","chapter":46,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 46:19","book":"Jer","chapter":46,"verse":19,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 30:13","book":"Ezk","chapter":30,"verse":13,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" Her tribal chieftains have led Egypt astray."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 2:16","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":16},{"label":"Jr 46:14","book":"Jer","chapter":46,"verse":14},{"label":"Jr 46:19","book":"Jer","chapter":46,"verse":19},{"label":"Ezk 30:13","book":"Ezk","chapter":30,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" has mixed within her a spirit of confusion."},{"kind":"text","text":" The leaders have made Egypt stagger in all she does,"},{"kind":"text","text":" as a drunkard staggers in his vomit."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"No head or tail, palm or reed, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 9:14–16","book":"Isa","chapter":9,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" will be able to do anything for Egypt."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 9:14–16","book":"Isa","chapter":9,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On that day Egypt will be like women and will tremble with fear because of the threatening hand of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies when he raises it against them. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The land of Judah will terrify Egypt; whenever Judah is mentioned, Egypt will tremble because of what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies has planned "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 5:19","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" against it."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 5:19","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On that day five cities in the land of Egypt will speak the language of Canaan and swear loyalty to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies. One of the cities will be called the City of the Sun. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss, DSS, Sym, Tg, Vg, Arabic; other Hb mss read of Destruction; LXX reads of Righteousness"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"= the ancient Egyptian city Heliopolis"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss, DSS, Sym, Tg, Vg, Arabic; other Hb mss read of Destruction; LXX reads of Righteousness"},{"marker":2,"text":"= the ancient Egyptian city Heliopolis"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On that day there will be an altar to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the center of the land of Egypt and a pillar to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" near her border. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 28:18","book":"Gen","chapter":28,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 24:4","book":"Exo","chapter":24,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 22:10","book":"Jos","chapter":22,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 22:26","book":"Jos","chapter":22,"verse":26,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 28:18","book":"Gen","chapter":28,"verse":18},{"label":"Ex 24:4","book":"Exo","chapter":24,"verse":4},{"label":"Jos 22:10","book":"Jos","chapter":22,"verse":10},{"label":"Jos 22:26","book":"Jos","chapter":22,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"It will be a sign and witness to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies in the land of Egypt. When they cry out to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" because of their oppressors, he will send them a savior and leader, and he will rescue them. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 3:9","book":"Jdg","chapter":3,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 3:15","book":"Jdg","chapter":3,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 6:7","book":"Jdg","chapter":6,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 10:10","book":"Jdg","chapter":10,"verse":10,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jdg 3:9","book":"Jdg","chapter":3,"verse":9},{"label":"Jdg 3:15","book":"Jdg","chapter":3,"verse":15},{"label":"Jdg 6:7","book":"Jdg","chapter":6,"verse":7},{"label":"Jdg 10:10","book":"Jdg","chapter":10,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" will make himself known to Egypt, and Egypt will know the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" on that day. They will offer sacrifices and offerings; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 56:7","book":"Isa","chapter":56,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 60:7","book":"Isa","chapter":60,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zch 14:16","book":"Zec","chapter":14,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" they will make vows to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" and fulfill them. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 56:7","book":"Isa","chapter":56,"verse":7},{"label":"Is 60:7","book":"Isa","chapter":60,"verse":7},{"label":"Zch 14:16","book":"Zec","chapter":14,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" will strike Egypt, striking and healing. Then they will turn to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", and he will be receptive to their prayers and heal them."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On that day there will be a highway "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 11:16","book":"Isa","chapter":11,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 35:8","book":"Isa","chapter":35,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 49:11","book":"Isa","chapter":49,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 62:10","book":"Isa","chapter":62,"verse":10,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" from Egypt to Assyria. Assyria will go to Egypt, Egypt to Assyria, and Egypt will worship with Assyria."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 11:16","book":"Isa","chapter":11,"verse":16},{"label":"Is 35:8","book":"Isa","chapter":35,"verse":8},{"label":"Is 49:11","book":"Isa","chapter":49,"verse":11},{"label":"Is 62:10","book":"Isa","chapter":62,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On that day Israel will form a triple alliance with Egypt and Assyria —a blessing within the land. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:19:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies will bless them, saying, “Egypt my people, Assyria my handiwork, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 100:3","book":"Psa","chapter":100,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 29:23","book":"Isa","chapter":29,"verse":23,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 45:11","book":"Isa","chapter":45,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 60:21","book":"Isa","chapter":60,"verse":21,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 64:8","book":"Isa","chapter":64,"verse":8,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:10","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":10,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" and Israel my inheritance are blessed.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 9:26","book":"Deu","chapter":9,"verse":26,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 9:29","book":"Deu","chapter":9,"verse":29,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:9","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":9,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 28:9","book":"Psa","chapter":28,"verse":9,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 47:6","book":"Isa","chapter":47,"verse":6,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 63:17","book":"Isa","chapter":63,"verse":17,"letter":"l"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 100:3","book":"Psa","chapter":100,"verse":3},{"label":"Is 29:23","book":"Isa","chapter":29,"verse":23},{"label":"Is 45:11","book":"Isa","chapter":45,"verse":11},{"label":"Is 60:21","book":"Isa","chapter":60,"verse":21},{"label":"Is 64:8","book":"Isa","chapter":64,"verse":8},{"label":"Eph 2:10","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":10},{"label":"Dt 9:26","book":"Deu","chapter":9,"verse":26},{"label":"Dt 9:29","book":"Deu","chapter":9,"verse":29},{"label":"Dt 32:9","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":9},{"label":"Ps 28:9","book":"Psa","chapter":28,"verse":9},{"label":"Is 47:6","book":"Isa","chapter":47,"verse":6},{"label":"Is 63:17","book":"Isa","chapter":63,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279542740}